<br>
Quick example... when we beastlords heard that monks had 18/20 fists at level 65 (I think that was the ratio), my first impulse was to say &quot;Wow, that's really cool.  I hope we get the same thing, or something close to it.&quot;  Never did I think &quot;That's too powerful, monks shouldn't get that if we don't.&quot;  It's a matter of perspective. <p><br><center><img src="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/notherkrag.jpg" width="500" height="200" border="0" usemap="#nothermap"><map name="nothermap"><area alt="Fury of Faith" coords="31,157,152,187" href="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/fury"><area alt="Tipop's Homepage" coords="186,157,321,187"  href="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/"><area alt="Kraggan's Magelo Profile" coords="342,157,465,186" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=120506"></map></center>
